sequenceDiagram
    participant M as Model LLM
    participant Q as Query Loop
    participant R as Tool Registry
    participant P as Permission Policy
    participant T as Tool Handler
    participant H as Post-tool Hooks

    Q->>M: messages + tool schemas
    M-->>Q: text 或 tool_calls[]

    alt 模型返回文本 无tool call
        Q->>Q: 终止循环 返回final_message
    else 模型请求 tool call
        loop 每个 tool_call
            Q->>R: execute(name, input, context)
            R->>P: check_before(tool, input)
            P-->>R: ✓ 或 ✗ 路径越界/NETWORK未审批/DELETE拒
            R->>T: handler(input, context)
            T-->>R: ToolResult(content, metadata)
            R->>P: check_after(tool, input, result)
            R->>H: run_post_tool_hooks(name, input)
            H->>R: 自动执行 check_truthfulness / check_ats / match
            R-->>Q: ToolResult + hook results
        end
        Q->>M: assistant message + tool results → 下一轮
    end
